stops with a continuable error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;**Â -Â ContinuableÂ Error
INTERN("*DOCUMENTATION*"):Â #&amp;lt;PACKAGE SYSTEM&amp;gt;Â isÂ locked
IfÂ youÂ continueÂ (byÂ typingÂ 'continue'):Â IgnoreÂ theÂ lockÂ andÂ proceed
TheÂ followingÂ restartsÂ areÂ alsoÂ available:
SKIPÂ Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â :R1Â Â Â Â Â Â skipÂ (COMPILE-FILES-IF-NEEDED-SERIALLYÂ #)
STOPÂ Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â :R2Â Â Â Â Â Â stopÂ loadingÂ file
/extra/sw/src/slime/swank-loader.lisp
ABORTÂ Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â :R3Â Â Â Â Â Â ABORT&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And after that, even if you continue slime is never able to connect to
